text: São Caetano do Sul-Prefeito Walter Braido, unofficially called only as São Caetano or São Caetano do Sul, is a train station on CPTM Line 10-Turquoise. The station is located in the center of the city of São Caetano do Sul, in the ABC Region. On January 2015, the then-called São Caetano station was renamed to São Caetano do Sul-Prefeito Walter Braido. ==References== Category:CPTM stations Category:Railway stations opened in 1883 Category:Railway stations opened in 1973
